- Need to read current `frontend/` chat components to confirm existing effect rendering structure before implementing #289
- Whether to use "silent unlock" vs "grayed-out teaser" for #290 depends on whether features are discoverable through other paths — issue text leans toward silent unlock but Primer recommends teasers for discoverability
