Issue #296 is a UX Overhaul EPIC. Through analysis, all sub-issues are implemented **except one**: the sidebar inline quick-add form (#280) is missing its optional `check-in date` and `parent project` fields. Issues #275, #276, #277, #279, #274 are fully implemented in the codebase (but still open in GitHub). This plan completes #280 by adding those two fields.

